#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.kregexpeditor.metainfo.xml:11
msgid "KRegexpEditor"
msgstr "KRegexpEditor"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.kregexpeditor.metainfo.xml:12
msgid "Edit regular expression"
msgstr "Editatu adierazpen erregularra"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kregexpeditor.metainfo.xml:14
msgid ""
"KRegexpEditor is a lightweight KDE application designed to help you create, "
"test, and refine regular expressions with ease. It provides an interactive "
"visual interface that highlights matches in real time, supports common regex "
"syntax features, and offers helpful tools to build complex patterns without "
"memorizing every rule."
msgstr ""
"KRegexpEditor adierazpen erregularrak erraz sortu, probatu, eta fintzeko "
"diseinatuta dagoen KDE aplikazio arin bat da. Ikus-interfaze elkarreragile "
"bat dakar bat etortzeak denbora errealean nabarmentzen dituena, adierazpen "
"erregularren sintaxi ezaugarriak onartzen dituena, eta arau guztiak buruz "
"ikasi beharrik gabe eredu konplexuak eraikitzeko tresna lagungarriak "
"eskaintzen dituena."
